<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天能放晴真是太好了。<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這可是難得的釣魚大會，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要玩得盡興喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然釣魚大會比的是釣到的魚的數量，<delay20 />
但你如果想釣到大魚，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就選在大影子附近出竿吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />順利釣到想要的魚的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也會覺得加倍地開心喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果一直釣不到魚的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />換個地方釣釣看，
也是不錯的選擇喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />隨著釣魚的地點不同，
能釣到的魚也會不一樣呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不曉得今天能釣到什麼魚<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我為了參加今天的釣魚大會，<delay20 />
還特別準備了新的個人專用釣竿呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管是運動還是釣魚，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我都是很講究用具的喔！<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為這樣感覺能釣到更多魚嘛，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">如果你想參加釣魚大會，<delay20 />
可以先去廣場<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />找<colour id="3" />俞司廷<colour id="65535" />聊聊喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>